The paper presents an algorithm for constructing a context-free grammar for an input string, which is a problem in data structures (cs.DS) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The algorithm also involves a transformation of the LZ77 factorization, which is related to information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the running time of the algorithm, which is a topic in algorithms and data structures (cs.SI).
